type `:set number` if yu cannot see line numbers
type `l` 6 times, so the cursor is under the I in MISTAH
type `x` 5 times to remove ISTAH
type `i` to enter insert mode
type `R.`
hit escape
type `$` to go to the end of the line
type `h` 2 times so the cursor is under the R in Schroedingr
type `i` to enter insert mode
type `E`
~~~the first line should now read:
DEAR MR, SCHROEDINGER,  ~~~~





hit escape
type `:%s/TEH/THE/g`

